# ForgeSight README demo. Regenerate with:  vhs docs/assets/demo.tape
Output docs/assets/demo.gif

Require uv

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1280
Set Height 540
Set Padding 22
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms

Hide
Type "uv sync --all-packages >/dev/null 2>&1; clear"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show

Type "uv run python examples/demo.py"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
